320
00:14:59,982 --> 00:15:01,525
- Yeah, sure.
- [narrator] <i>Sato is--</i>

321
00:15:01,525 --> 00:15:02,693
Yeah, sure!

322
00:15:02,693 --> 00:15:04,695
[Hitohito] Huh?
I didn't ask you anything yet.

323
00:15:04,695 --> 00:15:06,363
SOCIAL AND CULTURAL RESEARCH CLUB

324
00:15:06,363 --> 00:15:09,867
So do I do
what everyone asks of me too much?

325
00:15:09,867 --> 00:15:12,286
- Wait. You're asking us now?
- [Amami] Wha...?

326
00:15:12,286 --> 00:15:15,497
{\an8}You're right.
You would do almost anything, Sato.

327
00:15:15,497 --> 00:15:16,999
{\an8}So, can you give me your panties?

328
00:15:16,999 --> 00:15:18,125
{\an8}[Ushiroda] You're horrible.

329
00:15:18,125 --> 00:15:19,293
{\an8}Your mom's panties.

330
00:15:19,293 --> 00:15:21,503
{\an8}[Ushiroda] Her mom's panties?
That's worse.

331
00:15:21,503 --> 00:15:24,298
{\an8}- Uh, yeah, sure!
- [Ushiroda] Are you sure?

332
00:15:24,298 --> 00:15:26,467
You have got to learn to say no.

333
00:15:26,467 --> 00:15:28,886
Ugh. But, really,
it's just my mom's panties.

334
00:15:28,886 --> 00:15:30,596
- I can do that.
- [Ushiroda] No, you can't!

335
00:15:30,596 --> 00:15:31,805
Ugh.

336
00:15:31,805 --> 00:15:33,807
So let me help you practice saying no.

337
00:15:33,807 --> 00:15:36,185
I'm going to ask you to do something,
and you say no. Okay?

338
00:15:36,185 --> 00:15:37,394
Yeah, sure.

339
00:15:41,982 --> 00:15:44,401
[Ushiroda] You know,
my parents are in serious debt.

340
00:15:44,401 --> 00:15:45,944
