341
00:15:45,944 --> 00:15:48,072
What? Yes! I'll try to get you that!

342
00:15:48,072 --> 00:15:49,490
I'd do that for you, Eiko!

343
00:15:49,490 --> 00:15:51,659
[Ushiroda] I told you to say no!

344
00:15:52,242 --> 00:15:53,953
Then how about your grandmother's panties?

345
00:15:53,953 --> 00:15:56,664
You're still hung up on that?
You're a disgusting pervert!

346
00:15:56,664 --> 00:15:57,998
- Yeah, sure.
- Say no!

347
00:15:57,998 --> 00:16:00,959
[Ushiroda breathing heavily]

348
00:16:02,252 --> 00:16:06,548
Oh, it's just that being nice to others
feels really good, you know?

349
00:16:06,548 --> 00:16:09,426
That's why
I can't turn down people's requests.

350
00:16:09,426 --> 00:16:12,262
So is your great-grandmother still alive?
[grunting]

351
00:16:13,263 --> 00:16:15,182
If you keep doing
what everyone asks you to do,

352
00:16:15,182 --> 00:16:17,434
someone's going
to seriously trick you someday.

353
00:16:17,434 --> 00:16:20,229
And if you keep spoiling people,
they won't function on their own.

354
00:16:20,229 --> 00:16:23,190
Sato, sorry.
Can you hand me that ball over there?

355
00:16:23,190 --> 00:16:25,317
- [Amami] Yeah, sure!
- We're not done yet!

356
00:16:25,818 --> 00:16:27,820
[whimsical music playing]

357
00:16:29,279 --> 00:16:30,155
[Amami] Hmm.

358
00:16:30,155 --> 00:16:32,783
<i>Am I really being too nice?</i>

359
00:16:32,783 --> 00:16:36,078
- Hey, Sato? Can you help me hold this up?
- [Amami] Hmm?

360
00:16:36,078 --> 00:16:37,162
Yeah, sure.

