374
00:17:04,732 --> 00:17:05,941
Huh? I'm fine.

375
00:17:05,941 --> 00:17:08,485
This stack is actually heavier
than it looks.

376
00:17:08,485 --> 00:17:10,904
No problem! No prob! I'll be fine!

377
00:17:10,904 --> 00:17:12,781
Uh, wait. Hold on!

378
00:17:12,781 --> 00:17:15,826
{\an8}[straining] Komi,
if there's anything you want, just ask.

379
00:17:15,826 --> 00:17:16,994
{\an8}[Komi gasping]

380
00:17:16,994 --> 00:17:19,955
[Amami straining]

381
00:17:20,914 --> 00:17:21,915
