382
00:17:21,915 --> 00:17:22,833
[Amami gasping]

383
00:17:23,709 --> 00:17:26,086
{\an8}[Komi] S-Sato,

384
00:17:26,920 --> 00:17:28,088
you too.

385
00:17:28,088 --> 00:17:30,090
