400
00:18:01,872 --> 00:18:05,084
<i>I've never asked someone else
to do something for me.</i>

401
00:18:07,920 --> 00:18:09,046
[Amami grunting]

402
00:18:09,046 --> 00:18:10,714
[Amami] Um, Komi?

403
00:18:10,714 --> 00:18:11,632
[Komi grunting]

404
00:18:12,841 --> 00:18:15,761
Um, I... I come early every morning

