before class for everyone.

408
00:18:25,687 --> 00:18:28,774
And so then, as I think about it,

409
00:18:28,774 --> 00:18:30,109
no one has ever...

410
00:18:31,276 --> 00:18:34,655
<i>Well, I didn't know that asking people
to do something was so nerve-racking.</i>

411
00:18:35,781 --> 00:18:36,698
