00:19:58,322 --> 00:20:00,490
I won't tell you
how many moves you need to solve them.

445
00:20:00,490 --> 00:20:01,783
[upbeat music playing]

446
00:20:01,783 --> 00:20:02,701
[Komi grunting]

447
00:20:02,701 --> 00:20:06,413
Ah. You're right about the first move,
but for the next move...

448
00:20:06,413 --> 00:20:08,832
