453
00:20:22,346 --> 00:20:23,472
[Komi grunting]

454
00:20:24,056 --> 00:20:26,767
If you move the pawn,
it's going to come back anyway, right?

455
00:20:26,767 --> 00:20:28,226
Do you see my thinking?

456
00:20:28,226 --> 00:20:29,519
That would be pointless.

457
00:20:29,519 --> 00:20:30,437
[Komi grunting]

458
00:20:31,480 --> 00:20:32,689
[Mikuni] <i>Uh... huh?</i>

459
00:20:32,689 --> 00:20:36,401
Like I told you, if you move the rook,
you can do it in five moves.

460
00:20:36,401 --> 00:20:38,320
- [Mikuni] Uh...
- Don't you think?

461
00:20:38,320 --> 00:20:40,614
We've gotta move this piece
right over here.

462
00:20:40,614 --> 00:20:42,532
I told you that's the wrong move.

463
00:20:42,532 --> 00:20:44,910
