477
00:21:22,823 --> 00:21:24,199
[Najimi] Huh? [laughing]

478
00:21:24,199 --> 00:21:25,534
What's going on, you two?

479
00:21:25,534 --> 00:21:28,495
When did you become so close to each other
you started to fight?

480
00:21:28,495 --> 00:21:29,788
- [Hitohito] Hmm?
- [Komi gasps]

481
00:21:30,914 --> 00:21:31,832
[Hitohito] Uh...

482
00:21:33,125 --> 00:21:34,835
[both groaning]

483
00:21:34,835 --> 00:21:35,919
[narrator] <i>They blushed.</i>

484
00:21:35,919 --> 00:21:37,629
[ending theme music playing]

485
00:23:04,383 --> 00:23:05,217
{\an8}[music fades]

486
00:23:06,468 --> 00:23:07,928
[narrator] <i>Something extra.</i>

487
00:23:07,928 --> 00:23:11,098
The way Tadano thinks,
the game will go like this and then this.

488
00:23:11,098 --> 00:23:13,183
The gold general's going
to block the path.

489
00:23:13,183 --> 00:23:14,434
Oh, I gotcha.

490
00:23:14,434 --> 00:23:17,437
All I was thinking about
at that point was moving the king.

491
00:23:18,021 --> 00:23:19,022
[Mikuni chuckling]

492
00:23:19,022 --> 00:23:20,440
I'm sorry, Komi.

493
00:23:20,440 --> 00:23:22,818
I guess I did jump the gun.

494
00:23:23,318 --> 00:23:24,486
{\an8}SMUG

495
00:23:24,486 --> 00:23:27,239
{\an8}[narrator] <i>Komi is cute
when she has a smug look on her face too.</i>

496
00:23:27,239 --> 00:23:29,157
<i>Something even more extra?</i>

497
00:23:29,157 --> 00:23:31,660
Look who's here!
I brought Komi and Tadano!

498
00:23:31,660 --> 00:23:33,537
Hey, you three! It's good to see you.

499
00:23:33,537 --> 00:23:36,373
[Amami] I'm sure you already know
each other. This is Ushiroda.

500
00:23:36,373 --> 00:23:39,960
I sat in class behind you,
but we never got the chance to talk much.

501
00:23:39,960 --> 00:23:42,671
[Amami] And this is Maeda.
He sat in front of you.

502
00:23:43,547 --> 00:23:45,966
Komi, is your grandmother
still alive... [grunting]

503
00:23:46,508 --> 00:23:49,636
[narrator] <i>Seventy-three friends
left to go until one hundred.</i>

